text.tspan: Add amounts of colored sand to different sets of columns, so that it
fills every column right up to the flor level.
For each set, you can indicate how much sand to add, every how
many columns to add it, and what is the first column you add it to.
1 star: each column only needs one type of sand
2 stars: this version, with 3 types of sand
3 stars: more advanced, with 4 types of sand
